main.name: HJRES46
main.longTitle: JOINT RESOLUTION Relating to a national emergency declared by the President on February 15, 2019.
main.enactingFormula: Resolved by the Senate and House of Representatives of the United States of America in Congress assembled,

section.content: That, pursuant to section 202 of the National Emergencies Act (50 U.S.C. 1622), the national emergency declared by the finding of the President on February 15, 2019, in Proclamation 9844 (84 Fed. Reg. 4949) is hereby terminated.

signature.role: Speaker of the House of Representatives.
Vice President of the United States and President of the Senate.
